message: Hey Rohan! Weekly check-in. How's progress on your goals?
Hi Ruby, I've been following about 50% of the plan so far. Need some tweaks.
Let me take a look. What specific areas are you struggling with?
I'm curious about diet timing - should I eat before or after workouts? Also, which is better for mornings/evenings?
Great questions! Eating 30-60 minutes post-workout can help. Morning workouts might be better with a light snack beforehand.
Thanks, Ruby! What about nootropics and sleep supplements? Should I take them at the same time?
Nootropics are fine anytime, but consider taking sleep supplements 30-60 minutes before bed. Consistency is key!
Got it! What about intermittent fasting and exercise? Can I do both simultaneously?
Yes, you can do both! Just be mindful of your body's energy levels. Adjust as needed.
Hey Ruby, just a reminder that Rohan is traveling to Hong Kong this week for business. Need help with logistics.
Got it! I'll make sure to coordinate his schedule while he's away.
Hey team, just a friendly reminder that our test panel is after Week 36. Stay focused!
Hi Ruby, any updates on my plan?
Yes! I've made some adjustments based on your feedback. Let me send you the revised plan.
